           <div type="translation" source="bib:Chhom2011_01">
 	<p n="1-6">Sruk Vīrendra Kanloñ <gap reason="lost"/> Si Saṁ-ap, Si <gap reason="lost"/> , Si <gap reason="lost"/> , Si Khñuṁ, 36 male slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gho</foreign></supplied>, 26 animal keepers <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gvāl</foreign></supplied>, <gap reason="lost"/> female slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tai</foreign></supplied>, 22 male slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>lap</foreign></supplied>, 7 <foreign>tai a</foreign>, 12 boys at the age of running <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>si rat</foreign></supplied>, <gap reason="lost"/> girls at the age or running <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tai rat</foreign></supplied>, 27 baby boys <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>si pau</foreign></supplied>, 16 baby girls <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tai pau</foreign></supplied>; total 235. Among the lvan, there are 19 male slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gho</foreign></supplied>, 8 animal keepers <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gvāl</foreign></supplied>, 2 female slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tai</foreign></supplied>, a male slave <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>lap</foreign></supplied>; total 30.</p>
              <p n="6-8">Sruk Jeṅ Gnaṅ in the region of Vīrendra<gap reason="lost"/>: Si Kandhi, 6 male slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gho</foreign></supplied>, 2 animal keepers <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gvāl</foreign></supplied>, 7 female slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tai</foreign></supplied>, 2 boys at the age of running <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>si rat</foreign></supplied>, a baby boy <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>si pau</foreign></supplied>, a baby girl <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tai pau</foreign></supplied>; total 20. Among the <foreign>lvan</foreign>, there are 4 male slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gho</foreign></supplied>.</p>
              <p n="9-10">Sruk Kumarambha: Si Adan, 33 male slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gho</foreign></supplied>, 4 animal keepers <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>gvāl</foreign></supplied>, 24 female slaves <supplied reason="explanation"><foreign>tai</foreign></supplied>, 2 <foreign>tai a</foreign>; total 84.</p>
